description: Indian skipper Rohit Sharma emphasized the importance of putting pressure on bowlers in T20 cricket after India's 50-run win against Bangladesh in the ICC T20 World Cup Super Eights. He praised the team's aggressive play, adaptability to conditions, and the collective effort of all eight batters in achieving high totals.
title: In T20, we don't need fifties and hundreds: Rohit Sharma

description: Pat Cummins creates history with back-to-back T20I hat-tricks against Afghanistan, ensuring a strong start from the openers ends on a low. Afghanistan restricted to 148/6 in the T20 World Cup Super Eights clash at Kingstown, St Vincent.
title: Watch: Cummins first to take back-to-back T20I hat-tricks

description: Microsoft and Nvidia clash over AI chip design, with Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang controlling chip allocation. Tensions escalate as Nvidia dictates chip installation, leading to a feud with Microsoft CEO Satya Nadella's intervention.
title: How Satya Nadella may be key in solving Nvidia, MS ‘AI chip feud’

description: Section 144 imposed in Jodhpur after a communal clash at Eidgah. 51 arrested, stone pelting, fires, and clashes reported. Police deployed and situation under control.
title: Section 144 imposed, 51 arrested after communal clashes break out in Jodhpur

description: The test was conducted at the Aeronautical Test Range (ATR) at Challakere in Chitradurga district, some 220km from Bengaluru. The RLV project is an important programme that will demonstrate one of the technologies needed to meet India’s ambitions of sustained human presence in space. The RLV-LEX-03, built upon RLV-LEX-02, was aimed at improving the vehicle’s performance, guidance, and landing capabilities.
title: Isro's Reusable Launch Vehicle completes 3rd landing test, paving way for orbital re-entry

description: In a shocking case of female infanticide in Delhi, newborn female twins were allegedly murdered and buried by the family. Delhi Police exhumed the bodies and filed an FIR to book the accused.
title: ‘Unhappy’ with girls, Delhi family kills 2 newborns

description: Babar Azam and the Pakistan team faced intense criticism following their disappointing performance in the tournament, which saw them exit during the group stage. This criticism, which targeted Babar in particular, has left the captain disheartened.
title: Watch: 'Sirf aapke sentiments hurt huye...?': - Babar Azam slammed

description: Chief priest Acharya Laxmikant Dixit, who consecrated the Ram temple in Ayodhya, passed away in Varanasi. His last rites were performed at Manikarnika Ghat.
title: Ram temple event chief priest dies

description: Another of Rohit Sharma's 'precious gems' was caught on the stump mic during the India-Bangladesh Super 8 clash on Saturday. The incident occurred in the 14th over of the Bangladesh run chase when Kuldeep Yadav had just dismissed Shakib Al Hasan after being hit for a six.
title: Watch: 'Aada maarne de...' - Rohit's hilarious reply to Kuldeep
